<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <h1>LeetDreamer</h1>
  <p>A modular pipeline for generating narrated algorithm visualization videos.</p>

  <h2>Audio-First Approach</h2>
  <p>LeetDreamer uses an audio-first methodology: generate TTS audio, extract durations, then drive animation timing from those durations. This ensures narration and visuals stay perfectly synchronized.</p>

  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Modular adapter architecture for swappable components</li>
    <li>Schema-validated scene specifications</li>
    <li>Single source of truth controls both animation and narration</li>
    <li>Jinja2-powered animation templates</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Quick Start</h2>
  <pre><code>python build.py scenes/two_pointers/scene.json -v</code></pre>

  <p>See the <a href="/architecture">Architecture</a> page for details on how the pipeline works, or jump to <a href="/usage">Usage</a> to get started.</p>
</BaseLayout>
